psp_comb_long$dataset <- "p"

psp_comb_long <- 
  psp_comb_long %>% 
  dplyr::select(
    # district_plot_measurement, 
    plot_id    = district_plot,
    obs_date   = date_v,
    dataset,
    measure_year,
    binomial,
    obs,
    dem, edge, nbr, 
    understory = pt5to2,
    kurtosis   = zkurt,
    height90   = zq90
  )

ebird_comb_long <- 
  ebird_comb_long %>% 
  dplyr::select(
    # district_plot_measurement, 
    plot_id    = checklist_id,
    obs_date   = observation_date,
    dataset,
    measure_year,
    binomial,
    obs,
    dem, edge, nbr, 
    understory = pt5to2,
    kurtosis   = zkurt,
    height90   = zq90
  )

psp_comb_long
ebird_comb_long
combined_df <- bind_rows(psp_comb_long, ebird_comb_long)
mod_df <- 
  combined_df %>% 
  group_by(binomial, measure_year, dataset) %>% 
  tidyr::nest() 
## group_by: 3 grouping variables (binomial, measure_year, dataset)
mod_df <- 
  mod_df %>% 
  mutate(pa = map(data, find_the_best_pa_model)) 
mod_df <- 
  mod_df %>% 
  mutate(abu = map(pa, find_the_best_abu_model)) 
results_tb <- 
mod_df %>% 
  mutate(
    abu_mae = map_dbl(abu, function(x) mae_vec(
      truth    = x$test_complete$obs_abu, 
      estimate = x$test_complete$prediction_abu, 
      na_rm    = TRUE
      )),
    abu_low_obs = map_dbl(abu, function (x) max(x$n_obs))
    
  ) %>% 
  dplyr::select(
    binomial, dataset, measure_year,
    abu_mae,
    abu_low_obs
  )
## mutate (grouped): new variable 'abu_mae' with 53 unique values and 0% NA
##                   new variable 'abu_low_obs' with 30 unique values and 0% NA
results_tb %>% 
  filter(abu_low_obs >= 7) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = abu_mae, color = dataset)) +
  geom_density() +
  facet_grid(~measure_year) +
  scale_x_continuous(
    limits = c(0, 1)
  ) +
  labs(
    x = "Mean absolute error",
    y = "Frequency"
    ) +
  theme_ipsum_rc()
